00:09:55,678 --> 00:09:57,546
There's no way
we'll finish in time.

251
00:09:57,580 --> 00:09:59,281
Okay, I'll just
make a list of places

252
00:09:59,299 --> 00:10:01,483
she and I have been together,
and hope we luck out

253
00:10:01,518 --> 00:10:02,751
and find
the last clue.

254
00:10:02,786 --> 00:10:04,419
We'll split up,
cover more ground.

255
00:10:04,453 --> 00:10:05,504
Move.

256
00:10:10,126 --> 00:10:12,661
Hey, Kriss Kross,
can we change up the music?

257
00:10:12,695 --> 00:10:14,797
It kind of sounds like
the end of a movie

258
00:10:14,831 --> 00:10:16,148
