00:10:19,969 --> 00:10:21,003
Why don't
you rebound?

262
00:10:21,037 --> 00:10:24,072
Nobody here
compares to Millicent.

263
00:10:24,107 --> 00:10:25,174
Except maybe Jerry.

264
00:10:25,208 --> 00:10:28,510
Technically they share 50%
