of the snow globe museum,

270
00:10:50,934 --> 00:10:52,351
so I'm right
where I wanna be.

271
00:10:52,385 --> 00:10:55,938
Okay, um, my girlfriend
left a clue here, I think.

272
00:10:55,972 --> 00:10:57,673
Like, for a
scavenger hunt.

273
00:10:57,707 --> 00:11:00,209
