- Yes.

274
00:11:00,243 --> 00:11:03,045
She said you'd
be here by noon.

275
00:11:03,079 --> 00:11:04,446
Not doing so good.
All right, well.

276
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:06,081
Thanks, Kevin.
I'm supposed to tell you

